  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of Bilastine Ophthalmic Solution (0.2%,0.4%,0.6%) compared to
      vehicle for the treatment of the signs and symptoms of allergic conjunctivitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
